WEBVTT

00:00:35.930 --> 00:00:38.470
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.470 --> 00:00:41.270
=Episode 17=

00:00:42.375 --> 00:00:43.291
To be honest,

00:00:44.083 --> 00:00:45.416
three days ago,

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:47.458
I received a secret imperial order.

00:00:47.833 --> 00:00:49.458
His Majesty wanted to review

00:00:49.833 --> 00:00:51.916
all files related
to Prince Luo's case himself.

00:00:54.333 --> 00:00:56.125
I had no choice.

00:00:57.875 --> 00:01:00.250
His Majesty knows
about my father's case?

00:01:00.375 --> 00:01:01.916
His Majesty misses nothing.

00:01:02.291 --> 00:01:03.625
Of course he knows.

00:01:05.625 --> 00:01:06.625
I see.

00:01:07.666 --> 00:01:08.541
But Leng Xin...

00:01:08.583 --> 00:01:09.750
What about Leng Xin?

00:01:11.833 --> 00:01:12.500
Leng Xin

00:01:13.208 --> 00:01:14.333
has vanished without a trace.

00:01:14.875 --> 00:01:16.166
Who knows when we can catch him?

00:01:17.291 --> 00:01:18.333
Be patient.

00:01:19.291 --> 00:01:22.250
That villain will show himself
sooner or later.

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:24.333
When he does,

00:01:25.375 --> 00:01:27.041
I will make sure

00:01:28.750 --> 00:01:29.625
to reel him in.

00:01:33.458 --> 00:01:35.000
Leng Xin's secret file is gone.

00:01:35.375 --> 00:01:36.125
Not just Leng Xin's.

00:01:36.666 --> 00:01:38.000
The secret files

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:39.500
of many Bounty List fugitives
are gone too.

00:01:40.041 --> 00:01:41.416
In both the Southern
and Northern Bureaus,

00:01:42.375 --> 00:01:44.333
everyone seems to have two faces.

00:01:45.375 --> 00:01:47.791
Right and wrong, good and evil,
truth and lies...

00:01:48.875 --> 00:01:49.958
Do you think

00:01:50.083 --> 00:01:51.750
our ever-smiling Commander

00:01:52.625 --> 00:01:54.750
is hiding some secret of his own?

00:01:55.958 --> 00:01:58.791
It seems the Northern Bureau

00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:01.708
is as treacherous as it looks.

00:02:06.541 --> 00:02:07.000
Hua.

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:08.666
Whose files do you want to check?

00:02:08.916 --> 00:02:09.708
I have some.

00:02:11.041 --> 00:02:12.958
Do you have anything on Leng Xin?

00:02:13.333 --> 00:02:13.958
Leng Xin?

00:02:15.375 --> 00:02:16.125
I collected some.

00:02:19.180 --> 00:02:21.140
(Northern Bureau)

00:02:22.041 --> 00:02:22.625
(Leng Xin Files)
Duoyu.

00:02:23.500 --> 00:02:25.625
(Leng Xin Files)
Hua said you have files on Leng Xin.

00:02:26.375 --> 00:02:27.208
(Jinyiwei Classified Files)
I didn’t expect this many.

00:02:27.208 --> 00:02:28.310
(Jinyiwei Classified Files)

00:02:29.166 --> 00:02:30.041
Where did you get

00:02:30.041 --> 00:02:31.291
so many files on Leng Xin?

00:02:31.791 --> 00:02:33.375
I gathered many of them myself.

00:02:33.625 --> 00:02:35.458
Some are just rumors.

00:02:37.791 --> 00:02:38.625
These say

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:42.333
Leng Xin trained
under the Diancang Sect,

00:02:43.083 --> 00:02:45.666
then say he learned
from an overseas master.

00:02:46.375 --> 00:02:48.083
Half of this contradicts the other half.

00:02:48.875 --> 00:02:51.375
Some of it is hearsay.

00:02:53.541 --> 00:02:54.166
Duoyu.

00:02:55.666 --> 00:02:56.375
Why are you

00:02:56.750 --> 00:02:58.458
so interested in Leng Xin?

00:02:59.250 --> 00:03:00.041
Me?

00:03:01.291 --> 00:03:03.500
I have always wanted
to join the Jinyiwei.

00:03:03.916 --> 00:03:05.041
But my martial arts are poor,

00:03:05.416 --> 00:03:06.541
and I can never pass the physical test.

00:03:07.916 --> 00:03:08.916
So I thought,

00:03:09.958 --> 00:03:11.541
if I could catch Leng Xin,

00:03:12.083 --> 00:03:13.958
maybe the Northern Bureau
would make an exception for me.

00:03:14.625 --> 00:03:17.208
Maybe I would even become
a Baihu or a Qianhu.

00:03:17.666 --> 00:03:18.958
Then let us see who still dares
call me useless.

00:03:19.541 --> 00:03:20.416
I see.

00:03:22.125 --> 00:03:22.875
Can I borrow

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.291
these files and read them?

00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:25.708
Of course.

00:03:31.930 --> 00:03:34.520
(Chong'er Pavilion)

00:03:35.220 --> 00:03:40.810
(The killer is known as Leng Xin.)

00:03:40.810 --> 00:03:44.060
(Heartless, with unpredictable methods.)

00:03:51.220 --> 00:03:54.430
(Jinyiwei Classified Files)

00:04:14.458 --> 00:04:15.166
What are you doing here?

00:04:15.583 --> 00:04:16.125
I'm looking for someone.

00:04:16.500 --> 00:04:17.833
Then announce yourself first.

00:04:18.458 --> 00:04:19.916
You can’t just barge in here.

00:04:20.125 --> 00:04:20.791
What's wrong?

00:04:20.791 --> 00:04:21.500
Do you think this is a market?

00:04:22.666 --> 00:04:23.083
Young Master.

00:04:23.791 --> 00:04:24.541
He says he is looking for someone.

00:04:26.416 --> 00:04:27.375
Well, well.

00:04:27.500 --> 00:04:29.125
If it isn't "Mr. Handcuffs".

00:04:30.666 --> 00:04:31.500
Who are you looking for?

00:04:32.791 --> 00:04:33.958
I brought food for Bingfan.

00:04:35.250 --> 00:04:35.750
Chang Le.

00:04:36.791 --> 00:04:38.125
Tell him where he is.

00:04:38.208 --> 00:04:39.041
Chong'er Pavilion.

00:04:39.166 --> 00:04:39.916
And what kind of place is it?

00:04:40.041 --> 00:04:41.708
The finest restaurant in the capital.

00:04:42.416 --> 00:04:43.833
Do you think she will starve here?

00:04:44.125 --> 00:04:45.041
That is your business.

00:04:45.458 --> 00:04:46.083
Whether I bring food

00:04:46.666 --> 00:04:47.416
is my decision.

00:04:47.583 --> 00:04:48.833
Whether I let you in

00:04:49.083 --> 00:04:50.541
is mine.

00:04:52.416 --> 00:04:53.958
What if I force my way in?

00:04:56.666 --> 00:04:57.333
Can he?

00:05:00.500 --> 00:05:01.500
Try it.

00:05:03.375 --> 00:05:03.916
Young Master Chang.

00:05:08.166 --> 00:05:09.541
Constable Guan, what brings you here?

00:05:09.541 --> 00:05:11.500
I brought food for Bingfan.
Where is she?

00:05:11.666 --> 00:05:12.541
Then hurry.

00:05:12.708 --> 00:05:13.791
Bingfan locked herself in her room

00:05:13.791 --> 00:05:14.750
and read files all night.

00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:15.708
She still hasn't come out.

00:05:16.041 --> 00:05:17.041
She hasn't come out all night?

00:05:17.666 --> 00:05:19.375
Then she hasn't had food or water
since last night.

00:05:19.375 --> 00:05:20.583
Right. She wouldn't even open the door
for me.

00:05:20.916 --> 00:05:21.500
Chang Le, see him out.

00:05:23.916 --> 00:05:24.750
Don't follow me.

00:05:27.416 --> 00:05:28.083
Who is it?

00:05:29.890 --> 00:05:31.810
(Jinyiwei Classified Files)

00:05:32.333 --> 00:05:33.750
You haven't slept all night, have you?

00:05:36.958 --> 00:05:38.125
You must not have eaten
last night either.

00:05:38.458 --> 00:05:39.041
Are you hungry?

00:05:41.125 --> 00:05:43.708
Now that you mention it, I am.

00:05:47.875 --> 00:05:48.541
I made soup.

00:05:54.875 --> 00:05:55.375
Are you all right?

00:05:55.750 --> 00:05:57.250
My neck... My neck can't move.

00:05:57.250 --> 00:05:58.083
Don't move. I will massage it for you.

00:05:58.500 --> 00:05:59.750
You have been stiff for twelve hours.

00:05:59.958 --> 00:06:00.500
Let me help.

00:06:01.791 --> 00:06:02.791
Why are you touching her?

00:06:03.166 --> 00:06:04.291
She strained her neck.

00:06:04.458 --> 00:06:05.625
I have known massage since childhood.

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.500
Hurry. Bingfan said she was hungry.

00:06:12.375 --> 00:06:12.833
Eat while it is hot.

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:15.333
Have some soup.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.125
Thank you, Guan.

00:06:17.333 --> 00:06:17.666
Of course.

00:06:30.625 --> 00:06:31.208
You feel sick again?

00:06:32.916 --> 00:06:34.000
Is the soup undercooked?

00:06:34.750 --> 00:06:35.458
It can't be.

00:06:35.791 --> 00:06:36.916
I cooked it for four hours.

00:06:38.833 --> 00:06:40.125
It has nothing to do with Guan.

00:06:40.875 --> 00:06:42.250
I suddenly felt

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:43.458
dizzy

00:06:43.958 --> 00:06:44.958
and terribly nauseous.

00:06:45.375 --> 00:06:46.708
You were probably looking down too long,

00:06:46.916 --> 00:06:47.791
and it made you lightheaded.

00:06:55.625 --> 00:06:56.708
Today is your lucky day.

00:06:57.041 --> 00:06:58.541
I will show you

00:06:58.541 --> 00:07:01.083
the truest truth in the capital.

00:07:21.500 --> 00:07:23.166
You have a secret room in here?

00:07:24.708 --> 00:07:26.458
Why not shout it louder
so everyone knows?

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:28.458
Go in.

00:07:39.083 --> 00:07:39.625
Well?

00:07:50.166 --> 00:07:50.833
(Green Bamboo Sword?)

00:08:02.125 --> 00:08:04.333
You have this many files on Leng Xin?

00:08:05.083 --> 00:08:05.708
How?

00:08:06.041 --> 00:08:09.291
These days, money can buy anything.

00:08:10.083 --> 00:08:11.291
Do I look like a three-year-old?

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:12.916
Fine. I will tell you the truth.

00:08:14.416 --> 00:08:15.458
Zhang gave them to me.

00:08:16.166 --> 00:08:16.958
Zhang Weimin?

00:08:19.541 --> 00:08:20.166
Why?

00:08:21.708 --> 00:08:22.750
How would I know?

00:08:23.208 --> 00:08:24.166
But my guess is

00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:27.666
that Zhang Weimin said these files
had to be sealed away

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:30.041
and kept from government officers.

00:08:30.250 --> 00:08:31.708
I'm just an idle outsider,

00:08:32.250 --> 00:08:34.583
so giving me a copy is fine.

00:08:36.666 --> 00:08:38.708
You people really are bold.

00:08:39.416 --> 00:08:41.291
You even play word games
with His Majesty.

00:08:43.125 --> 00:08:43.625
So?

00:08:45.083 --> 00:08:45.958
With all these files,

00:08:47.625 --> 00:08:48.916
you will have plenty to read
for a while.

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:17.680
(He kills without mercy,
becoming a demon in every heart.)

00:09:34.180 --> 00:09:41.080
(Leng Xin's skills are extraordinary.)

00:10:05.208 --> 00:10:05.500
Hey.

00:10:06.791 --> 00:10:08.083
This is not proper.

00:10:08.500 --> 00:10:10.250
You come to Chong'er Pavilion
with a food box every day.

00:10:10.333 --> 00:10:11.333
People who don't know better

00:10:11.458 --> 00:10:12.708
will think our food is terrible.

00:10:13.583 --> 00:10:15.041
I am here to bring food to Bingfan.

00:10:15.416 --> 00:10:16.875
Not if it hurts our good name.

00:10:17.583 --> 00:10:19.208
You Chong'er Pavilion
people are so fussy.

00:10:19.583 --> 00:10:20.083
Where is Bingfan?

00:10:20.583 --> 00:10:21.583
Miss Shen

00:10:22.541 --> 00:10:23.916
is in our young master's room.

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:29.208
Hey!

00:10:29.666 --> 00:10:31.541
Barging in again?
Do you have no manners?

00:10:35.850 --> 00:10:37.930
(This claim remains unverified.)

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:41.708
I discovered Leng Xin's secret.

00:10:42.958 --> 00:10:43.583
What did you find?

00:10:44.208 --> 00:10:44.833
What secret?

00:10:46.250 --> 00:10:47.458
Every time Leng Xin acts,

00:10:48.250 --> 00:10:49.166
it is not for money.

00:10:49.458 --> 00:10:50.625
They're actually summoned

00:10:50.625 --> 00:10:52.125
by a jade token with this pattern.

00:11:15.458 --> 00:11:15.791
Right.

00:11:16.875 --> 00:11:18.958
But who holds this jade token

00:11:18.958 --> 00:11:19.625
and what it is

00:11:19.875 --> 00:11:20.625
remains unknown.

00:11:24.375 --> 00:11:25.750
Still, this is a major discovery.

00:11:28.375 --> 00:11:29.333
Do you think

00:11:30.041 --> 00:11:30.750
Feng Fuliu

00:11:30.875 --> 00:11:33.416
keeps stealing fine jade
from noble houses

00:11:35.166 --> 00:11:36.458
because of this?

00:11:37.541 --> 00:11:40.208
That is for you to find out.

00:11:42.208 --> 00:11:42.916
There are too many leads.

00:11:43.208 --> 00:11:44.458
I need to sort them out one by one.

00:11:45.083 --> 00:11:45.625
But

00:11:46.333 --> 00:11:47.458
this is already a major breakthrough.

00:11:49.041 --> 00:11:50.500
You must be tired after reading
for so long.

00:11:50.583 --> 00:11:51.416
You need a break.

00:11:51.916 --> 00:11:52.458
Are you hungry?

00:11:53.041 --> 00:11:54.000
Actually, yes.

00:11:55.791 --> 00:11:56.208
Let's go.

00:11:56.583 --> 00:11:57.375
I will take you to eat something good.

00:11:58.375 --> 00:11:58.791
Okay.

00:11:59.875 --> 00:12:00.291
Put it down.

00:12:02.125 --> 00:12:02.458
Let's go.

00:12:03.970 --> 00:12:06.560
(Go with the Flow)

00:12:10.125 --> 00:12:10.875
Guan.

00:12:17.625 --> 00:12:18.666
Are you done discussing the case?

00:12:20.083 --> 00:12:20.958
Do you need me?

00:12:21.625 --> 00:12:22.125
No.

00:12:23.375 --> 00:12:24.333
I just came to see you.

00:12:27.041 --> 00:12:28.500
We are going to eat. Come with us.

00:12:31.458 --> 00:12:31.875
No need.

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:33.041
You two go ahead.

00:12:35.416 --> 00:12:36.333
I only came to see you.

00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:00.791
Who is that? What a grand entrance.

00:13:00.791 --> 00:13:02.166
With that kind of procession,

00:13:02.416 --> 00:13:04.833
it must be someone
from the imperial clan.

00:13:11.208 --> 00:13:12.666
Your Highness, forgive us
for not greeting you sooner.

00:13:12.708 --> 00:13:13.708
Please forgive us.

00:13:14.708 --> 00:13:16.608
Princess Pingyang?

00:13:16.808 --> 00:13:18.708
(Princess Pingyang)
Is he here?

00:13:18.875 --> 00:13:20.000
Yes. He is.

00:13:20.958 --> 00:13:21.625
I want to see him.

00:13:27.458 --> 00:13:28.333
This way, Your Highness.

00:13:33.041 --> 00:13:34.291
She is no ordinary guest.

00:13:35.625 --> 00:13:36.625
Come on. Let's take a look.

00:13:38.416 --> 00:13:39.583
To this day, no one knows

00:13:39.583 --> 00:13:40.750
Leng Xin's true identity.

00:13:42.125 --> 00:13:43.791
Whether male or female, how old,

00:13:44.125 --> 00:13:44.958
who trained him...

00:13:45.375 --> 00:13:46.625
It is all guesswork.

00:13:48.750 --> 00:13:50.500
Judging by when they first appeared,

00:13:52.458 --> 00:13:53.750
they should be around thirty.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.958
And that jade token
used to summon them...

00:14:01.375 --> 00:14:02.208
Young Master!

00:14:18.541 --> 00:14:19.083
Come here.

00:14:21.291 --> 00:14:22.750
Your second wife is here.

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:24.500
In the private room upstairs.

00:14:25.083 --> 00:14:25.625
What?

00:14:26.333 --> 00:14:26.958
Your second wife.

00:14:27.833 --> 00:14:28.333
Who?

00:14:30.291 --> 00:14:31.208
Princess Pingyang.

00:14:33.625 --> 00:14:34.666
Why didn't you stop her?

00:14:40.541 --> 00:14:41.083
Bingfan.

00:14:41.583 --> 00:14:42.416
An old friend is here.

00:14:42.458 --> 00:14:43.875
I will see her, then come back to you.

00:14:45.208 --> 00:14:45.791
Keep reading.

00:14:45.916 --> 00:14:46.333
Okay.

00:14:48.125 --> 00:14:49.958
Say that again, and I will hit you.

00:14:50.833 --> 00:14:53.250
Chang Huan, you really are asking
for a beating.

00:14:53.250 --> 00:14:53.875
I would not dare.

00:14:54.375 --> 00:14:54.958
Bingfan.

00:14:56.083 --> 00:14:56.541
Bingfan.

00:14:57.958 --> 00:14:58.541
Bingfan.

00:14:58.750 --> 00:15:00.166
Do you know who came
to Chong'er Pavilion?

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:01.958
Young Master Chang's friend.

00:15:04.166 --> 00:15:05.666
But it is Princess Pingyang.

00:15:06.958 --> 00:15:08.333
Princess Pingyang?

00:15:08.875 --> 00:15:10.041
She is Young Master Chang's friend too?

00:15:11.416 --> 00:15:12.208
I'm not sure.

00:15:12.458 --> 00:15:13.458
But Hua said

00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:15.500
Young Master Chang's background
is no simple matter.

00:15:16.916 --> 00:15:18.500
Princess Pingyang is so noble,

00:15:18.833 --> 00:15:20.458
yet she came all the way here
to see him.

00:15:20.708 --> 00:15:23.375
That proves he is no ordinary man.

00:15:24.958 --> 00:15:27.625
Feng Fuliu harassed me recently

00:15:28.083 --> 00:15:29.541
and nearly got me killed.

00:15:30.083 --> 00:15:32.000
Feng Fuliu steals treasures.
He does not hurt people.

00:15:32.666 --> 00:15:34.375
But I was still scared.

00:15:34.875 --> 00:15:36.291
And you were so heartless.

00:15:36.458 --> 00:15:37.875
You did not even send someone
to check on me.

00:15:39.416 --> 00:15:40.500
Don't talk to me like that.

00:15:40.875 --> 00:15:41.458
It makes my skin crawl.

00:15:42.625 --> 00:15:44.375
When I entered the palace
the day before yesterday,

00:15:44.708 --> 00:15:46.166
the Empress Dowager asked

00:15:46.708 --> 00:15:48.166
about our engagement.

00:15:48.791 --> 00:15:50.250
When did we ever get engaged?

00:15:50.833 --> 00:15:52.875
Our families arranged it
when we were children.

00:15:53.250 --> 00:15:54.666
Are you going to deny it now?

00:15:56.208 --> 00:15:56.958
Pingyang.

00:15:57.458 --> 00:15:59.375
That was something the elders agreed on.

00:16:00.125 --> 00:16:01.250
I never agreed to it.

00:16:02.333 --> 00:16:03.625
Besides, you are a princess.

00:16:04.041 --> 00:16:04.916
Born to wealth and rank.

00:16:05.208 --> 00:16:06.708
You can choose any husband you want.

00:16:06.708 --> 00:16:08.458
Why waste your time

00:16:08.875 --> 00:16:10.583
on a useless man with no office or rank?

00:16:10.833 --> 00:16:12.000
What is the point?

00:16:12.250 --> 00:16:14.333
You are descended from one
of the six founding dukes,

00:16:14.458 --> 00:16:15.625
the Duke Zheng line.

00:16:16.041 --> 00:16:17.833
You are the current heir to Duke Zheng,

00:16:17.833 --> 00:16:19.375
Young Duke Chang Beiming.

00:16:19.625 --> 00:16:20.958
And you call yourself useless?

00:16:21.166 --> 00:16:22.291
Who do you think you are fooling?

00:16:22.625 --> 00:16:23.750
Duke Zheng?

00:16:25.458 --> 00:16:26.041
Bingfan.

00:16:26.458 --> 00:16:26.958
He... he...

00:16:27.208 --> 00:16:27.458
He...

00:16:28.583 --> 00:16:29.500
He what?

00:16:30.708 --> 00:16:32.166
Young Master Chang
really is no ordinary man.

00:16:32.541 --> 00:16:34.708
He is a descendant of Chang Yuchun,
Prince Kaiping,

00:16:35.458 --> 00:16:37.041
and of Chang Mao, Duke Zheng,

00:16:37.041 --> 00:16:39.375
one of the six dukes of the Hongwu reign.

00:16:39.458 --> 00:16:41.458
He is the current heir to Duke Zheng.

00:16:42.041 --> 00:16:42.666
No wonder.

00:16:44.250 --> 00:16:45.708
No wonder Marquis Taiping

00:16:45.708 --> 00:16:46.791
looked like a mouse before a cat.

00:16:48.291 --> 00:16:49.041
Bingfan.

00:16:49.791 --> 00:16:51.208
There is one more bombshell.

00:16:52.708 --> 00:16:53.208
What?

00:16:53.791 --> 00:16:54.416
Well...

00:16:55.250 --> 00:16:56.916
Young Master Chang and Princess Pingyang

00:16:57.500 --> 00:16:59.000
have been engaged since childhood.

00:17:02.416 --> 00:17:06.083
By rights, man should
take the initiative.

00:17:06.750 --> 00:17:08.166
But you have always been careless,

00:17:08.625 --> 00:17:10.291
and if I don't push you,

00:17:10.791 --> 00:17:12.958
you will never take this seriously.

00:17:13.958 --> 00:17:17.166
So yesterday, I went
to your family manor.

00:17:18.875 --> 00:17:20.166
Why did you go to my home?

00:17:21.125 --> 00:17:22.333
My father is stationed in Datong.

00:17:23.083 --> 00:17:23.916
My mother is at home.

00:17:24.500 --> 00:17:25.958
My brother has been ill for years.

00:17:26.166 --> 00:17:27.208
Why would you bother them?

00:17:27.458 --> 00:17:29.458
I only went to pay my respects
to your mother.

00:17:29.625 --> 00:17:30.791
She said

00:17:31.291 --> 00:17:33.500
this matter is still yours to decide.

00:17:34.416 --> 00:17:34.916
Pingyang.

00:17:35.583 --> 00:17:36.666
That was truly just

00:17:37.125 --> 00:17:39.375
drunken talk between our elders.

00:17:40.125 --> 00:17:41.208
There is no need to take it seriously.

00:17:42.291 --> 00:17:43.333
You want to break the engagement?

00:17:45.208 --> 00:17:46.250
I never agreed to it.

00:17:46.458 --> 00:17:47.708
How can I break what never existed?

00:17:48.125 --> 00:17:50.458
Chang Beiming, how dare you betray me?

00:17:51.250 --> 00:17:51.791
I...

00:17:52.166 --> 00:17:53.541
I will report you to His Majesty.

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:55.750
Go ahead. I'm not afraid.

00:17:57.000 --> 00:17:58.291
You have someone you like?

00:17:58.458 --> 00:17:59.250
Yes, I do.

00:18:00.166 --> 00:18:01.916
I love her so much.

00:18:02.083 --> 00:18:02.791
Who is she?

00:18:03.416 --> 00:18:04.708
Tell me that wretch's name.

00:18:04.916 --> 00:18:06.125
Don't call her that.

00:18:06.875 --> 00:18:07.250
I...

00:18:07.833 --> 00:18:09.333
I will tell the Empress Dowager.

00:18:11.791 --> 00:18:12.625
Just you wait.

00:18:13.208 --> 00:18:13.833
I'm back.

00:18:20.083 --> 00:18:22.791
Chief Squad Leader Cheng Xintian
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau

00:18:23.125 --> 00:18:23.958
greets the Young Duke.

00:18:41.720 --> 00:18:44.890
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:45.260 --> 00:18:48.640
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:48.890 --> 00:18:51.890
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:51.890 --> 00:18:55.300
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:18:56.390 --> 00:18:59.600
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:00.010 --> 00:19:03.350
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:03.930 --> 00:19:06.140
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:06.140 --> 00:19:10.180
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:10.180 --> 00:19:14.050
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:14.050 --> 00:19:17.800
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:18.100 --> 00:19:20.010
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:20.010 --> 00:19:24.550
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:24.850 --> 00:19:26.350
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:26.350 --> 00:19:28.720
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:32.600
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:32.600 --> 00:19:34.930
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:34.930 --> 00:19:39.930
♪And run toward this vast life♪